old Wilson's Labour Party \n | last=Vaughn |first=James R.\n | journal=Israel Affairs \n | year=2015 \n | volume=21 \n | pages=1\u201325\n | url= https://www.researchgate.net/publication/273313408\n | ref=harv\n}}\n*{{Cite book|title= Ernest Bevin\n | last =   Weiler | first = Peter\n | publisher = [[Routledge]]\n | year =2016\n | origyear =1993\n | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=ydEeDAAAQBAJ&pg=PT195 \n | isbn=  978-1-317-19842-0 \n | ref =harv\n}}\t\n*{{cite news  | title=Dalyell steps up attack on Levy \n | last=White | first=Michael \n | newspaper=[[The Guardian]]\n | date=6 May 2003 \n | url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2003/may/06/race.politics \n | ref =harv\n}}\n*{{Cite book|title= From Ambivalence to Betrayal: The Left, the Jews, and Israel \n | last =    Wistrich | first = Robert S.\n | author-link =  Robert S. Wistrich \n | publisher = [[University of Nebraska system|University of Nebraska Press]]/[[Vidal Sassoon International Center for the Study of Antisemitism]]\n | year =2012\n | url =   https://books.google.com/books?id=yBvt4Fwc5XoC&pg=PA205\n | isbn=  978-0-803-24083-4 \n | ref =harv\n}}\n*{{cite news| title=Labour funding crisis: Jewish donors drop 'toxic' Ed Miliband \n | last =Wright|first =Oliver\n | newspaper= [[The Independent]]\n | date= 9 November 2014\n | url =https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/labour-funding-crisis-jewish-donors-drop-toxic-ed-miliband-9849299.html\n | ref =harv\n}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite news |last=Asthana |first=Anushka |title=Labour antisemitism inquiry will not seek evidence from Ken Livingstone |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/may/16/labour-antisemitism-inquiry-shami-chakrabarti-not-seek-evidence-from-ken-livingstone |accessdate=30 November 2017 |work=The Guardian |date=16 May 2016 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news |last=Bodkin |first=Henry |title=Labour 'too tolerant' of anti-Semitism&nbsp;\u2013 new poll |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/08/1